{"tid":1405122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去親遊行/集會都係一個人或者搵唔到人陪？","createTime":"2019-08-04T07:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:13:39.000Z","uid":139919,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2302222c2d2450c8fc653fb0f1bceb27431860","tid":1405122,"uid":139919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"我..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨著而加啲黑警成日咁樣亂咁攻擊人<br />\n我唔敢再自己一個人行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奈何身邊好多都係啲只有立場但唔會行動嘅人..<br />\n屌佢地都屌唔郁..<br />\n而會行動嘅好多都住好遠<br />\n好似聽日罷工咁 佢地有佢地去佢地個區<br />\n我就得一個人去我個區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想係到搵啲成日都搵唔到人陪<br />\n或者成日都一個人出集會嘅手足<br />\n多個人一齊行可以保障到大家先 有個照應"},{"pid":"da7d87a63d7b6812386ea56f5812e36325d401b3","tid":1405122,"uid":258447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:51:40.000Z","msg":"你係咩區"},{"pid":"915a612c1b1c148535e5fd27ee84e0e4288b2c07","tid":1405122,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2302222c2d2450c8fc653fb0f1bceb27431860","tid":1405122,"uid":139919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"我..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨著而加啲黑警成日咁樣亂咁攻擊人<br />\n我唔敢再自己一個人行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奈何身邊好多都係啲只有立場但唔會行動嘅人..<br />\n屌佢地都屌唔郁..<br />\n而會行動嘅好多都住好遠<br />\n好似聽日罷工咁 佢地有佢地去佢地個區<br />\n我就得一個人去我個區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以